Class NSMPProcess

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class NSMPProcess
extends EdgeThread
    This class processes PGM database and makes SAC/V0 files for NSMP 
     arg    Parm   Description
 -b    yyyy,doy The ending day to process - all data in the year before will be checked
 -h    my.sql   Use this database server instead of one in MetaDBServer property
 -sendhost sf.host Use this host to do a sendFileII
 -sendport port Use this port to do a SendFileII
